metadata.name: Welcome To Our World!
metadata.description:
Our first ever collaboration work!

Bringing together two different art styles into one.
The combination of pop and contemporary art with some crypto/web3 things, and also we have Thai culture as the main attraction.

The concept that we bring is to make this illustration look like a strange girl who came from another world is on her way to Paery's world.

We can see another girl appeared as if to welcome her and wanted to introduce how beautiful the world she was currently visiting.

Illustration by arsnzip & Paerytopia
